ons.htm Parsons, Elsie Clews]{{spaced ndash}}1923: Capeverdian Stories; book 1: English, book 2: Creole)\n* ''Mornas \u2013 Cantigas Crioulas'', [[Eug\u00e9nio Tavares|Tavares, eug\u00e9nio]]{{spaced ndash}}1932\n* ''Renascen\u00e7a de uma civiliza\u00e7\u00e3o no Atl\u00e2ntico m\u00e9dio'' ([[Lu\u00eds Romano de Madeira Melo|Melo, Lu\u00eds Romano de Madeira]]{{spaced ndash}}1967: Collection of poems and stories in Portuguese and in Creole)\n* 100 Poemas{{spaced ndash}}Gritarei, Berrarei, Matarei, N\u00e3o vou para pas\u00e1rgada [[Ov\u00eddio Martins|Martins, Ov\u00eddio]], 1973{{spaced ndash}}Poems in Portuguese and in Creole\n* ''Negrume/Lzimparin'' (Melo, Lu\u00eds Romano de Madeira{{spaced ndash}}1973: Stories in Creole with Portuguese translation)\n* \"Textos crioulos cabo-verdianos\"  ([[S\u00e9rgio Frusoni|Frusoni, S\u00e9rgio]]{{spaced ndash}}1975) in ''Miscel\u00e2nea luso-africana'' coord. Valkhoff, Marius F.\n* ''Vang\u00eale cont\u00f3d d'n\u00f4s m\u00f3da'' (Frusoni, S\u00e9rgio : Fogo{{spaced ndash}}1979; Novo Testamento)\n* ''A Po\u00e9tica de S\u00e9rgio Frusoni \u2013 uma leitura antropol\u00f3gica'' (Lima, Mesquitela; Lisboa{{spaced ndash}}1992)\n</small>\n\n== External links ==\n{{incubator|kea}}\n\n;Linguistic texts\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070825024159/http://www.prio.no/private/jorgen/cv_kriollanguage.html Criol language]\n* [http://www.bela-vista.net/Creole.htm Creole grammars and dictionaries from Cape Verde]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20050618085010/http://www.clubetabanka.com/cv/creole.asp A Perspective on Capeverdean Crioulo] by [[Robert French]]\n* [https://www.researchgate.net/publication/249941077_Vowels_as_a_morphological_tool_in_Santiago_Creole_Portuguese_Cape_Verde Santiago Creole]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20050514091321/http://www.instituto-camoes.pt/cvc/bvc/bibbreve/006/bb06.pdf Literaturas Africanas] (African literatures in the Portuguese language and Portuguese creoles, pdf: in Portuguese)\n* [https://web