{"title_page": "Blackbear discography", "text_new": "{{Infobox artist discography\n|Artist          = [[Blackbear (musician)|Blackbear]]\n|Image           = \n|Caption         = \n|Studio          = 4\n|Singles         = 23\n|Option          = 5\n|Option name     = Promotional singles\n|1Option         = 2\n|1Option name    = Mixtapes\n}}\n\nThis is the discography of [[blackbear (musician)|Blackbear]] (Matthew Tyler Musto), an American rapper, singer, songwriter, and record producer.\n\n==Discography==\n\n===Studio albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" | Album details\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"6\" | Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" | Certifications\n|- style=\"font-size:smaller;\"\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;\"| [[Billboard 200|US]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/music/blackbear/chart-history/billboard-200|title=Blackbear \u2013 Chart history (Billboard 200)|work=Billboard|accessdate=December 5, 2017}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Top R&B/Hip-Hop Albums|US<br />R&B]]<br><ref name=R&BA>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/blackbear/chart-history/r-b-hip-hop-albums|title=Blackbear \u2013 Chart history: Top R&B/Hip-Hop Albums|work=Billboard|accessdate=November 28, 2017}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;\"| [[Canadian Albums Chart|CAN]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/blackbear/chart-history/canadian-albums|title=Blackbear Chart History: Canadian Albums|work=Billboard|accessdate=May 7, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;\"| [[MegaCharts|NLD]]<br><ref name=\"Hung Medien\">{{cite web|url=http://dutchcharts.nl/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Blackbear|title=Discografie Blackbear \u2013 dutchcharts.nl|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=April 28, 2017}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;\"| [[Official New Zealand Music Chart|NZ]]<br><r